<br>
Being a necro, I have never enjoyed free roam through basically anywhere, but i have the ability to go anywhere. As i lvl, I can go more and more places with little worry at all.<br>
<br>
Almost all evil characters have some form of night vision.  No night vision. .basicaly sucks. I love walking around the tunnels with no light and seeing everything.  I never have to worry about time. I just can't stand to not beable to see.<br>
<br>
As an dark elf i dont' have to worry about how i act. I can easily roleplay being quiet(how i am anyway) I can lash out at people(in rp,) i can mess with them, and i can even be nice to everyone.  <br>
<br>
As a necro, I am powerfull, as i mentioned before i can go where ever i want.  I tend to be a loner, so i can solo when i want.  But i am also a great filler of roles in groups. I can add melee damage, snare, fear, transfer mana, heal, and in a bind set myself up to do cr.<br>
<br>
Almost all my other characters are evil as well.  We are better tanks, int casters, clerics, shamens, etc etc. . . <br>
We never look like fire hydrants or tin cans. .<br>
<br>
I'll be a light race rogue, cause i can look dark elf, or iksar.  The same with bard.  <br>
<br>
Either way, i always seem to re-roll any character that has &quot;good&quot; blood in em.     <p><center>
